See e.g. <a href="http://debbugs.gnu.org/cgi/bugreport.cgi?bug=11401" rel="nofollow">http://debbugs.gnu.org/cgi/bugreport.cgi?bug=11401</a> for a discussion."</pre><pre><br></pre><pre>I'm going to comment that line out in <span style="font-family: Menlo; font-size: 11px;">ompi/mca/io/romio/romio/configure.ac so the trunk can build until someone figures out (a) if it is really needed, and (b) how to correctly add it</span></pre><pre><span style="font-family: Menlo; font-size: 11px;"><br></span></pre><pre><span style="font-family: Menlo; font-size: 11px;">Ralph</span></pre><pre><span style="font-family: Menlo; font-size: 11px;"><br></span></pre><pre><br></pre><pre>
